{"tid":755504,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足睇過cowboy bebop呢套動畫","createTime":"2018-07-25T09:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T15:35:08.000Z","uid":58841,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"09ecae015bb62a9c8073b805495fc1e18503b4a1","tid":755504,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"1998年既原創動畫<br />\n之前一直有聽講過呢部野係令到日本正式打入歐美市場既杰作<br />\n全世界評分網站長期前三（頭兩名好似係攻殼機動隊同CLANNAD）<br />\n但我近排去睇發現真係神作黎<br />\n渡邊監督 菅野配樂 入面mix哂唔同風格 西部牛仔乜鳩都有<br />\n打鬥場面毫無廢話連篇<br />\n結局完美<br />\n個人好撚鐘意追狗仔 spike回憶殺同埋對住長生不老既細路個幾part<br />\n真心建議各位去睇一下<br />\n首op好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/171819_3fb846a515cf5b0271f8c40abbe17c31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F171819_3fb846a515cf5b0271f8c40abbe17c31.png&h=f393d8c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"045335d72a257e406a326e22df7ede19c9b0a228","tid":755504,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"套野入面好重香港元素<br />\n背景真係演釋出90年代香港咁<br />\n配樂仲要每集無重複咁濟<br />\n歡迎樓下接受反駁"},{"pid":"b06749b156c90d6ecb5c1042d6957803ab392dba","tid":755504,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:32:26.000Z","msg":"結局好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acbe2338be6713aee5586c1496db4b55c88e35c","tid":755504,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"睇過渡邊 lupin the third , d 畫風真係好唔慣<br />\n呢個都係咁？"},{"pid":"f151e864cd6a534cd0d1b754e0767cd217453c9c","tid":755504,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"045335d72a257e406a326e22df7ede19c9b0a228","tid":755504,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:26:41